            "caption": "",
            "heading": "KIDS EVERTEE - THAT GROWS AS THEY DO",
            "text": "<p>Evertee Kids grows with your child, saving you money with unlimited replacements for their current and next size. </p><p>Made from tough, c<strong>omfy 100% organic cotton,</strong> it’s the only t-shirt they’ll need, leaving fast fashion in the dust. <strong>Grab yours today!</strong></p>",
